data.description: SELLER OFFERING $2500 IN CLOSING COST CREDIT TO BUYER with Acceptable offer! Bring all offers now and secure this…Dream getaway at this picturesque lake property nestled on the shores of Sardis Lake. This home offers a unique combination of natural beauty and modern conveniences. Situated on a generous 2.1-acre lot, this property boasts a tankless water heater for endless hot showers and energy efficiency. This prime location backs up to an expansive 14,360 acres of Corp. land. With public access, outdoor enthusiasts will relish in ample opportunities for hunting and exploration. Rest assured, your lake view will remain unobstructed, as the property is strategically positioned to prevent any future development. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of a private stocked pond, perfect for fishing and relaxation. Whether you seek a peaceful retreat, an outdoor adventure, or a combination of both, this lakefront oasis offers the ultimate escape. Don't miss the chance to make this slice of paradise.
